Sales Analysis

2020-2023

Edie

Introduction

This report presents a detailed analysis of sales data from 2020 to 2023. The analysis is based on the data stored in the MySQL data warehouse and aims to provide insights into the top-performing products, sales trends per quarter, and sales performance by country and sales representatives.

Analytical Query I: Top Five Products with the Most Sales Across All Years

The following analysis identifies the top five products that generated the most revenue over the entire period.
